title: Donald Trump points out 9/11 happened under George Bush, Jeb Bush freaks out
text: When Islamic terrorists attacked the United States on 9/11, President George W. Bush was the commander-in-chief. Republican front runner Donald Trump pointed this information out, and backlash quickly resulted from another top presidential candidate. Photo by Chip Somodevilla/Getty Images
